Media Relay is a multi-platform application that lets you manage dedicated display devices with minimal setup. Quickly upload photos, videos, gifs, weblinks and create slideshows from your phone or PC and control playback remotely.

Common use cases
•	Digital picture frames
•	Art exhibitions and galleries
•	Information kiosks and signage
•	Tabletop RPG map projection
•	Storefront advertising

Available on:
•	Google Play
•	Microsoft Store

For enterprise deployments requiring macOS or iOS management, contact the developer for support and licensing options.

NOTE: THIS IS NOT CASTING

media is transferred and stored on the target device for local playback, making it suitable for installations where persistent content is required.